OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a chilly feeling day
OL,6,Ffor all, but also bright with some
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Some heavy, blustery
OL,8,Fshowers are possible, mainly in the
OL,9,Feast, with a risk of hail. A brisk
OL,10,Fnortherly wind adding to the colder
OL,11,Ffeel.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers easing but a few
OL,14,Fpersisting overnight with the brisk
OL,15,Fnortherly wind continuing. Feeling
OL,16,Frather chilly, especially in the wind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
